WEBVTT

00:54.090 --> 00:56.210 line:80%
How did the plaintiff die?

00:56.770 --> 00:57.710 line:80%
My Lord,

00:57.760 --> 00:59.130 line:80%
when I found Fan Daniu,

00:59.130 --> 01:00.050 line:80%
he had already stopped breathing.

01:00.050 --> 01:01.320 line:80%
There were multiple knife wounds
on his body.

01:01.320 --> 01:03.220 line:80%
It looks like
he was hacked to death with a long knife.
